OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1776715554
OL,3,CPolice 'never' thought they would find
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe in storm drain
OL,6,FNoah, a pupil at St Malachy's College,
OL,7,Fwas found on June 27 2020 six days
OL,8,Fafter leaving his home in south
OL,9,FBelfast on his bike to meet two
OL,10,Ffriends in the Cavehill area of the
OL,11,Fcity.
OL,13,FA post-mortem examination found the
OL,14,Fcause of death was drowning.
OL,16,FRetired inspector Menary, who managed
OL,17,Fthe PSNI hazardous environment search
OL,18,F(HES) team, told jurors: "Our
OL,19,Foperation was to rule out any
OL,20,Flikelihood Noah was in or near the
OL,21,Fculvert."
OL,26,@zD@ZOU}D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
