FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1776715554
OL,3,CPolice 'never' thought they would find
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe in storm drain
OL,6,FDonal Lunny KC, the barrister
OL,7,Frepresenting the PSNI at the hearing,
OL,8,Fasked Mr Menary about a statement
OL,9,Fgiven by a constable involved in the
OL,10,Fsearch and rescue efforts who said he
OL,11,Fwas tasked with looking for human
OL,12,Fremains around or in the culvert.
OL,14,FMr Menary said a "bad choice of words"
OL,15,Fhad been used in the statement as
OL,16,F"recovering human remains was never,
OL,17,Fever an option, it was never our
OL,18,Fpurpose".
OL,20,F"We thought 'he is never going to be
OL,21,Fdown here'," he added.
OL,26,@vD@ROUvD@fO]xD@AOUzD@HO]|D@AOU}D@LO]
